{"type": "article", "id": 28787, "title": "移动梳妆台", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-28T06:53:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121527GownUsySaN04WDKh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>浴室里不够放化妆品怎么办？比利时的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/CamilleDescombes\">Camille Descombes</a> 以解决收纳问题为初衷，设计了一款名为 LEON 的移动化妆台。上半部分的木盒一共有四个大小不一的收纳空间，下半部分是两条带有滚轮的木腿和涂上黑漆的金属支架，两种材质的融合在视觉上带给人一种微妙的平衡感。支架的一部分向上延伸穿过木盒，在顶部配置了一面圆镜，另一侧则做了弧形的设计，可以用来推动化妆台移动。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215250fNiEjwRmBtAzCc6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215253Q1ScMACfavnUpwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121526Xi2H7nAerUd1IEaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121526RvhOuymlfSxpw7BE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}